l/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n李鴻章個陣都有搞軍備<br />\n咪又係一鑊熟 炒哂車<br />\n歴史一直在重演</blockquote><br />\n炒哂船先岩"},{"pid":"4efaa3613f0eca5fc4403b5b33ded257dd01eea5","tid":93221,"uid":11359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T08:11:34.000Z","msg":"快d 8國聯軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再割地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2590b498f50bc90c30aad4a1117588e449b27506","tid":93221,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T08:11:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>歷史一直在重複</blockquote><br />\n因為人心不變，如果制度上無變歷史重演係必然</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n人心已經變左<br />\n<br />\n以前清朝 民間有革命黨, 官場有維新派<br />\n<br />\n家陣中國, 不論是平民定官員, 都只係想用盡方法搵錢, 再移民去外國<br />\n革命?? 維新?? 不了"},{"pid":"157e8fcb3eefa09385365b48620463c736bf55ba","tid":93221,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T08:23:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0f4ea9eda43c2847cb594f3ff36a708efd35c7b2","tid":93221,"uid":40839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T09:08:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n001A仲係複製緊遼寧號 002可以有幾先進<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n李鴻章個陣都有搞軍備<br />\n咪又係一鑊熟 炒哂車<br />\n歴史一直在重演</blockquote><br />\n炒哂船先岩</blockquote><br />\n買先進來佬貨都炒 證明輸既唔係軍備 而係制度同人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d63a593cead16e23eec7964a97bb894cb86bc9af","tid":93221,"uid":35702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T10:12:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中共同清朝一樣, 都係以保護政權 做最終目標.......國家強唔強大,根本唔重要<br />\n<br />\n就好似 清末時期, 當時國家積弱, 最需要係改革<br />\n<br />\n但清朝高層 擔心改革.....會令到政權不穩, 所以情願國家繼續積弱, 都要阻止改革</blockquote><br />\n中共積唔積弱我唔知<br />\n我只知中共同清未唔同的是<br />\n中共積極搞軍備<br />\n清未積極搞派場<br />\n<br />\n只能說<br />\n<br />\n搞軍備實無死</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而家既支那軍備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 買架三手爛鬼航母</blockquote><br />\n你知不知002 起緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/001A%E5%9E%8B%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA%E6%AF%8D%E8%88%B0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F001A%25E5%259E%258B%25E8%2588%25AA%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E6%25AF%258D%25E8%2588%25B0&d=lpQc3k9qqopqOWg%2BlinPr5kBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=07b19d58\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/001A%E5%9E%8B%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA%E6%AF%8D%E8%88%B0</a> 依一堆垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n001用滑躍起飛<br />\n個奸15油箱載量減半，拆淨幾枝飛彈先至夠輕起飛<br />\n未入到交戰範圍就冇油要回航<br />\n俾多三架航母你都唔係戰力啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n002 003吹到有蒸汽彈射<br />\n打撚晒飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除左老美冇人做到實淨耐用嘅蒸汽彈射<br />\n俄佬果條蒸汽彈射射十零次就要修理一次<br />\n即係彈射左一個中隊就要修理<br />\n老共煉金差咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你條軌有幾耐用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n順帶一提<br />\n降落用果套鋼索係英國貨<br />\n暫時未有'自主研發'<br />\n真係開打俾人禁運就冇得降落要飛單程啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b3c1b98c0db9eeb8619ff286413ea22e3f2bf5d","tid":93221,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T12:24:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而家既支那軍備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 買架三手爛鬼航母</blockquote><br />\n你知不知002 起緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n001A仲係複製緊遼寧號 002可以有幾先進<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n至少有彈射"},{"pid":"1f4d943f43d00baf5eca7c46e1c6fa7bb114137d","tid":93221,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T12:25:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n你知不知002 起緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n001A仲係複製緊遼寧號 002可以有幾先進<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n李鴻章個陣都有搞軍備<br />\n咪又係一鑊熟 炒哂車<br />\n歴史一直在重演</blockquote><br />\n政府有無出盡奶力先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b5c51174a864f301aaa88f0ed8d8ea729fadd3e","tid":93221,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T12:31:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/PwWY2YP.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FPwWY2YP.jpg&d=lpQc3k9qqopqOWg%2BlinPr5kBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=21b19722\" target=\"_blank\">http://i.imgur.com/PwWY2YP.jpg</a>"},{"pid":"ff708e2f135c09d25977d09251808f93f88afc0a","tid":93221,"uid":51859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T12:56:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">應戰的北洋艦隊已是四洋海軍中實力最強者，但無論火力、噸數、航速等仍比不上日本聯合艦隊</span><br />\n<br />\n上面編野無撚野下嘛？<br />\n北洋水師先進同勁過當年既聯合艦隊好撚多<br />\n定遠鎮遠果堆係亞洲最強既艦黎<br />\n<br />\n係人既問題先咁廢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n定遠號鎮遠號來佬貨 號稱亞洲最強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n清國廢撚到一隻比人炸沉 一隻比人偷埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n日本也是買進口船，不過人家的staff認真訓練。"},{"pid":"2287f5f36c9a8fa98724d2d7f7ba2d5d0b5a3418","tid":93221,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T13:08:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"38a1a61cf86fda0949c5d9ec3541236b60d392eb","tid":93221,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T13:16:32.000Z","msg":"而家成日喺亞洲蝦蝦霸霸， 得閒搞吓台灣， 日本， 新加坡， 菲律賓， 實出事， 雖然你死你事， 但至怕要我哋陪葬"},{"pid":"81474c45d139a71e377313de790895b4386ded41","tid":93221,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T13:21:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>土匪黨過唔過到2017年都成問題！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中共介有排捱<br />\n<br />\n外國無心推翻中共<br />\n中國人又無能力推翻中共</blockquote><br />\n咪係囉， 成日旨意咩支爆，內亂<br />\n根本冇可能， 你估共產黨傻咩<br />\n共產黨係每時每刻都諗點會保護自己政權<br />\n基本上冇大型戰爭好難推冧佢"},{"pid":"cfa0eedac9ee30f4a9c1c9eb61e5ac39a8f05ef0","tid":93221,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T03:41:57.000Z","msg":"行緊遠交近攻，<br />\n<br />\n交南非南美<br />\n<br />\n然後身邊所有國家都想中國仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc4562627b1dada3313d3b657dde6ebd088fb3fc","tid":93221,"uid":53589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T03:54:20.000Z","msg":"唔覺<br />\n中共對成個國家既監控根本強過滿清極多<br />\n每個職級同地方都有相應既黨組織相連同監控<br />\n全國所有野根本上比共產黨玩哂<br />\n清朝根本做唔到<br />\n地方主義同1911年各省可以獨立就係最好證明"},{"pid":"d395decc897f48d46360e239194b9a7378cc1545","tid":93221,"uid":2247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T03:59:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大航海時代禁海，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大數據時代禁網</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最致命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb7bb283c16bcf442f4f6e844ad0f9d681a92cec","tid":93221,"uid":59641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T04:11:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔覺<br />\n中共對成個國家既監控根本強過滿清極多<br />\n每個職級同地方都有相應既黨組織相連同監控<br />\n全國所有野根本上比共產黨玩哂<br />\n清朝根本做唔到<br />\n地方主義同1911年各省可以獨立就係最好證明</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我都覺得中共唔會冧，甚至我希望佢千祈唔好冧，冇咗中共㩒住十四億人周圍走成個亞洲都出事。<br />\n<br />\n最好中共繼續衰弱落去但又封鎖自己愈嚟愈嚴就perfect"},{"pid":"2e424076f4845035e22cb56847055cb0aee63a18","tid":93221,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T04:17:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>大航海時代禁海，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大數據時代禁網</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最致命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實佢自己鎖國打飛機係無問題，咁咪留喺自己裡內打飛機囉<br />\n唔會搵唔到食<br />\n但依家又出黎搞呢搞路，無料扮四條仲要自己打飛機吹到世界第一強國 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n戇鳩無極限咁想點"}]}